entries.journal_entry_description: Go to the source of the remote signal, find proof of the Diktat's innocence, and defeat the leaders behind this plot.
entries.journal_entry_title: Go to the Source of the Remote Signal
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Go to the source of the remote signal and deal with what you find there.
entries.task00_journal_entry_title: Go to the Source of the Remote Signal
entries.task01_journal_entry_description: Infiltrate the rogue Corsec base, defeat their leaders, and find proof of the Diktat's innocence.
entries.task01_task_display_string_3: Find Proof on the Rogue CorSec Computers
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Return to Lt. Jasper and fill him in on the latest events. You defeated 2 rogue CorSec commanders and found the proof necessary to completely absolve the Diktat of any accusations of illegal smuggling.
entries.task04_journal_entry_description: Search for proof that they have been attempting to frame the Diktat and his administration of smuggling spice. Look for it in one of their computer terminals.
entries.task05_journal_entry_description: Defeat Commander Hiram Bish of the rogue CorSec. He's somewhere within their base.
entries.task06_journal_entry_description: Defeat Commander Mtara Vinram of the rogue CorSec. She's somewhere within their base.
